description: Erection of a series of buildings comprising a 26 storey tower, with ground floor mezzanine (maximum height 92.95m AOD), and 9 individual buildings ranging from 4 to 8 storeys in height to provide 668 residential units, 958sqm of retail (Class A1, A2 and A3), and 268sqm of community use (Class D1), creation of a new open space and construction of new roads, pedestrian and cycle routes and new access to the highway, together with associated works including the provision of public cycle facility, basement car parking for 166 cars and cycle parking, servicing, landscaping and plant areas.
